dct_title_s: To the Honourable Thomas Penn and Richard Penn, Esqrs., true & absolute proprietaries & Governours of the Province of Pennsylvania & counties of New-Castle, Kent & Sussex on Delaware this map of the improved part of the Province of Pennsylvania
dct_description_sm: Facsim. of: Philadelphia : sold by the author, Nicholas Scull, 1759. Relief shown pictorially. Shows county boundaries.
